	<title>Jamestown</title>

  <para>Írta Rosanna Yuen</para>

          <sect2><title>Beállítás</title>


  <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <tbody>
	<row>
	  <entry>A pakli típusa</entry>
	  <entry>Szabványos pakli</entry>
	</row>
	<row>
	  <entry>Stock</entry>
	  <entry>
	    Top left pile.  All cards are placed here at beginning of
	    play.
	  </entry>
	</row>
	<row>
	  <entry>Tabló</entry>
	  <entry>
	    Nine piles in a 3x3 formation.  Each Tableau pile is dealt
	    one card face up.
	  </entry>
	</row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

          </sect2>
        <sect2><title>Cél</title>

  <para>
    Remove all cards.
  </para>

          </sect2>
        <sect2><title>Szabályok</title>

  <para>
    Remove pairs of cards with the same rank.  Empty piles are
    automatically filled from the Stock.
  </para>

          </sect2>
        <sect2><title>Pontozás</title>

  <para>
    Removing each pair of cards scores two points.
  </para>
  <para>Lehetséges legnagyobb pontszám: 52</para>

          </sect2>
        <sect2><title>Stratégia</title>

  <para>
    Remove pairs of cards as fast as possible.  That is the only challenge.
  </para>
        </sect2>
</sect1>
